{"tid":1205190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察最後搜不出什麼，在鄺議員和群眾壓力下向青年道歉","createTime":"2019-06-11T17:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T17:38:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0329434cbbc55357de43acab97dd96642275eb","tid":1205190,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%AD%B8%E5%A0%82%E7%84%A1%E6%95%99%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%A6%AE%E8%B2%8C-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A0%2582%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E8%25B2%258C-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%2599%2F&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=3a9f6845\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A0%2582%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E8%25B2%258C-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%2599%2F&h=1cc05333\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%AD%B8%E5%A0%82%E7%84%A1%E6%95%99%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%A6%AE%E8%B2%8C-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%99/</a><br />\n<br />\n通往立法會大樓的路上越夜越多人，兩個戴口罩的年輕人被警察喝停要搜身。<br />\n<br />\n一批警察把兩人圍着，卻惹來四周群眾注意，指摘警察濫權。群眾越聚越多，增援的警察也越來越多。有人通知鄺俊宇到來，鄺問警察搜身的理據，警察話懷疑有攻擊性物品。例如乜呢？𠝹刀、螺絲批呀，群眾起哄。<br />\n<br />\n其間有一拿著東森新聞咪牌女記者高舉手機想拍攝，卻擠不進去。有人說，係台灣記者，讓開畀佢影。另一市民用港腔國語說：「來看看一國兩制吧。」跟著大家七嘴八舌，「不要讓韓國瑜當選。不會發大財。」「凡是親中的都是騙子。」<br />\n<br />\n警察最後搜不出什麼，在鄺議員和群眾壓力下，向青年道歉，悻悻然離去。<br />\n<br />\n群眾拍手，一位阿嬸大聲說「學堂無教警察禮貌，香港人教」，其他人紛紛互叫「香港人加油！」<br />\n<br />\n報告完畢。<br />\n<br />\n#6.12全民野餐<br />\n#香港人真係好正<br />\n#the world is watching <br />\n#咁郭台銘呢<br />\n#警察要怪就怪林鄭<br />\n<br />\n（原刊作者 facebook，標題為編輯所擬）"},{"pid":"301f1a89195b998232cedf560968bbe44b56194d","tid":1205190,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:27:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"></span>"},{"pid":"3328a1c1cdd2fd4201d81e66561e54400c8e4db9","tid":1205190,"uid":36901,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"有人說，係台灣記者，讓開畀佢影。<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢到好心up<br />\n30年前北京市民叫群眾讓開俾香港記者影<br />\n30年後,我地終於體會到1989年北京市民既心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173d83c1cdf80ea002e0b9c962775cacfb03f15e","tid":1205190,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"佢好難解釋到點樣合理懷疑<br />\n一班年輕人出現喺地鐵站就係合理懷疑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f7a2b3dcea9743c27188c8bd59fc25a3dabad3","tid":1205190,"uid":49669,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:34:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">來看看一國兩制吧</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f32083689badb18632a5674dea0e27d2c60325f","tid":1205190,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173d83c1cdf80ea002e0b9c962775cacfb03f15e","tid":1205190,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"佢好難解釋到點樣合理懷疑<br />\n一班年輕人出現喺地鐵站就係合理懷疑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:38:45.000Z","msg":"而家係咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後生已經係原罪咁<br />\n屌你老母"}]}